Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.63,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice. I can see the \Npicture forming in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:14.91,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.91,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can we have them do our music?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.28,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.90,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:23.25,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I only know them from online, but...
