Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.57,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,They've been releasing tracks through \Nmusic sites for a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:32.55,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,and have worked on indie \Nanime and movies before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.89,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki, is that tan going to be a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:38.69,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It could've been,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:41.63,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't been doing any \Nmodeling jobs lately, so no sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:43.11,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Any offers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:45.73,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure. Haven't been really \Nkeeping up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.50,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Three of a kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:53.07,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki, could you accept the \Noccasional modeling job from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.43,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And watch the tan lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.94,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about, Kanamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:01.49,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think the eizouken's \Nnumber one selling point is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:03.95,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Refined and carefully-crafted animation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.46,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mizusaki's fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:11.92,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, she will be animating \Nuntil her hands fall off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:12.77,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,They'll fall off?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:16.47,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But the stardom of the model Tsubame Mizusaki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:20.34,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,dimming would be like having \None of our wings clipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:23.49,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, here's a promotional \Nplan that Mr. Kashima
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:27.04,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,from the dandan noodle shop just sent over.
