Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.65,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Voice actor auditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.74,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the judge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.84,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Once the idea was proposed \Nto the chamber of commerce,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:37.36,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,they enthusiastically agreed, thinking it'd\N be good advertising for the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.26,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.24,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You could have the starring role.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.02,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Except I know you'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:45.42,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I'm asking for your \Nhelp with this instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.67,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll take it over being in the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.59,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them know, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.17,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And if we're going to secure \Nmusic and have auditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.17,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,it'd help to know what the \Nstory was going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:57.81,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,A party!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.68,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing that music, I was \Ninspired to make our finale into a dance scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:05.21,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's a party! That seems fun! I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:07.12,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to be animating to music,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:09.94,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,we'll need to get an early demo \Nof the music for the dance scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.05,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why exactly are they partying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.83,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.94,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Celebration for a hard-won victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.52,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,"Inspired." "Maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:21.58,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like you're just \Nsubmitting scenes you thought up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.89,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,with no thought to the overall picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.05,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what the actual story is,\Nbut it's about time you—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.85,Default,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's lively in here, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:36.96,Default,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,Having a little party, Kanamoney?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Kanamoney!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:41.90,Default,Dotonbori,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.10,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think of another excuse to fine us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.01,Default,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.81,Default,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,You've always got your mind on cash, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.52,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's not money that I like, \Nit's productive activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:53.94,Default,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,And the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.94,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The money helps quantify that productivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.95,Default,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's a little problem with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:08.95,Default,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,Turns out, the school isn't thrilled \Nabout you making money on the outside.
