Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.32,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Kanamoney, once you're \Ndirecting your third production,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.03,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,you start to understand what the people want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.83,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And where are we with the story, Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.16,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Got it right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:06.51,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy prisoner of war comes \Nto understand human kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:12.17,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,changes sides, and fights \Nalongside humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.75,sign_14612_226_Soldier_smiles__,Storyboard direction sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(105,330,105,-20)\N}Soldier smiles,\Nbut can't talk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.47,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Can I stop you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:29.14,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What does the enemy look like?\N And who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.18,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,They're in UFOs, so they've \Ngotta be aliens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.57,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,P-Probably?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:37.33,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy fortress appears \Nout of Lake Shibahama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.82,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and has the same kind of design \Nas the human towers. Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.53,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, why were the UFOs attacking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.81,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are they invading the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.75,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.93,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your directions dictate what \Nthe entire staff is doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:56.33,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can fret your weird head off,\N but the clock is ticking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.97,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If the storyboards take too long, that puts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.09,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,extra pressure on every \Nother step in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.22,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.93,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.17,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Asakusa melted her way into hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:10.94,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.36,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the Sound Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:14.94,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Open sesame!
