Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.20,sign_16399_247_Fully_Rotated,Bolt signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz14.3\fax0.02\pos(383,196)\fs16}Fully Rotated
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.20,sign_16399_247_Fully_Rotated,Bolt signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz14.3\fax0.02\pos(277,78)\fs14}Fully Rotated
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.59,sign_16627_250_Rrrrrumble___,Snoring sign,0000,0000,0000,,Rrrrrumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.66,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like we were lost in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.66,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.33,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,A kappa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.51,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,No. Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.09,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,You sounded like you were \Nfiring a beam in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.60,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Like you'd see in a space battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.31,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sound in a vacuum, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.32,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wheel, dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:51.39,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.77,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is it Saturday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.58,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is today t-tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.78,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Today is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.49,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.70,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow from yesterday, which was Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.37,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's still Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:07.28,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man... so it's not tomorrow yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.98,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Did you seriously think a whole day \Npassed while you were asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.29,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've never napped before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.50,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that was a lifetime first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.49,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Were you doing something on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.51,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.83,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.61,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you want to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:34.44,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why exactly are we meeting up on bikes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.58,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're going sound hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.98,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hunt some sounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.97,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Work on the storyboards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:44.89,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And figure out who the bad guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.24,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you tagging along on a sound hunt?!\N That's the audio director's job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:50.82,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The general director's job is \Nto keep an eye on everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:54.24,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Talk big after you finish \Nyour own damn job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:57.15,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been fine on \Nmy own, but she insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.58,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:00.46,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You clearly don't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.50,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.23,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No ifs, ands, or buts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.08,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.69,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, not still! Moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.65,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm just looking for \Nideas for the storyboards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:10.37,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hunt of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.69,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.19,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Scenario hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.53,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted one last idea to put a \Nbow on the setup for the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.55,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind the company, \Nas long as you help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.25,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.03,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.49,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let'sa go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.49,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This had better be productive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.91,sign_19505_299_Missing,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-89.37\pos(301,108)}Turn on Lights
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.71,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.59,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the remains of a generator...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.93,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,With English brick bonding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.58,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.62,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've been curious about \Nthis place for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:23.01,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And this has something to do \Nwith the Shibahama-UFO Battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.01,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.57,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,No roof, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.94,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The idea is the water comes down and \Nturns a wheel, which generates power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.35,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool!
