Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.11,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's the clock tower \Nthat we're always looking at!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.84,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting to catch a glimpse up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.11,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the things I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.03,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda like a tourist spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.02,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! It's a pendulum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.74,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this place was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:58.06,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Looks to me an awful lot like an alien \Nbase disguised as a clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:01.25,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big! And you can \Nsee the back of the clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.90,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wager the owners or some \Npolitician thought they'd
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.33,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,fix the place up and turn it \Ninto a tourist destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.93,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This building just gave me an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:16.10,sign_21841_335_Twelve,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz11.04\fax-0.14\move(305,40,305,-10)}Twelve
