Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.61,sign_31146_451_________________,Signs; descending,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(140,320,140,5)\3c&HB0C9E7&}Jet\NSometimes depicted as going up\N and down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.90,sign_31146_451_________________,Signs; descending,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(495,360,495,5)}Range of rotation is \N90 degrees, won't turn \Nall the way at once
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:43.40,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And the water responds in kind by \Ngranting the surface world its blessing.
