Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.99,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This device is what enables \Nthat mutual exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:45.99,sign_31146_451_________________,Signs; descending,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(60,360,60,70)\3c&H86BBAA&}Output
