Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.99,sign_31146_451_________________,Signs; descending,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(195,360,195,200)\3c&HFCFBFC&}Input
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:49.01,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The tradition behind it is eventually forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:51.41,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but the technology itself evolves \Ninto becoming the basis for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.95,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,clockwork machinery, and is passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.72,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And the bells?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.23,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Festival rites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:57.75,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,They purify people of their evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.10,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and call upon the water for a bountiful harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:11.85,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The chime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:00.73,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:04.27,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Does this have anything to \Ndo with our current project?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:06.52,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Did you figure out how to connect this to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:08.62,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're really gonna need \Nto decide on the villains,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:10.71,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,or I won't be able to make \Nmuch progress with the sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:14.12,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What about the climax? Have you figured \Nout the identity of the bad guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:15.11,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:19.00,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And what are they after?! I thought you \Nwere gonna put a bow on the concept?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:27.61,main,Sakaki,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that they're in their own world, too.
